5
00:01:01,186 --> 00:01:05,148
Sometimes I wonder if my
life really didn't begin

6
00:01:06,441 --> 00:01:10,237
until I had my first child.

7
00:01:11,363 --> 00:01:15,325
[RUTH] And everything
else was just training.

8
00:01:16,743 --> 00:01:20,706
The same miracle plays out
every day all over the world.

9
00:01:23,458 --> 00:01:27,379
Not just a baby being born. It's a family.

10
00:01:38,223 --> 00:01:40,725
[RUTH] Jeff and I were
high school sweethearts,

11
00:01:40,726 --> 00:01:44,228
