biggest or the fastest,

30
00:02:45,374 --> 00:02:48,669
or the highest jumper on the floor.

31
00:02:49,169 --> 00:02:52,546
[RUTH] What my boy had was vision.

32
00:02:52,547 --> 00:02:55,257
