351
00:21:11,812 --> 00:21:14,148
I need your help... get your coat.

352
00:21:20,613 --> 00:21:23,615
It's okay dad. It's okay.

353
00:21:23,616 --> 00:21:24,866
Hang in there buddy. Hang in there.

