355
00:21:45,387 --> 00:21:49,349
[engine struggles to start]

356
00:21:49,350 --> 00:21:52,269
Please God! PLEASE!

357
00:21:54,355 --> 00:21:57,357
[JEFF] Don't go to sleep! You
gotta hang in there with me son!

358
00:21:57,358 --> 00:21:59,568
You gotta stay awake!

