365
00:22:22,424 --> 00:22:24,133
[MAN] Just get in.

366
00:22:24,134 --> 00:22:25,594
Start her up.

367
00:22:32,268 --> 00:22:33,519
Come on!

368
00:22:36,730 --> 00:22:38,566
Come on!

369
00:22:41,777 --> 00:22:44,779
