446
00:27:55,174 --> 00:27:57,508
Umm... we just can't graft
or put a plate there.

447
00:27:57,509 --> 00:28:01,429
Over time soft tissue will
fill the gap, but until then

448
00:28:01,430 --> 00:28:03,181
