449
00:28:03,182 --> 00:28:05,266
would be catastrophic.

450
00:28:05,267 --> 00:28:08,060
No sports... basketball?

451
00:28:08,061 --> 00:28:09,270
<i>No.</i>

452
00:28:09,271 --> 00:28:11,105
[RUTH] Can the tumor come back?

453
00:28:11,106 --> 00:28:13,399
Well... there's always that possibility

454
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:15,067
so we'll have to monitor it,

455
00:28:15,068 --> 00:28:18,029
and probably for the rest of his life.

456
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:21,365
But the good new is... he's going to have

457
00:28:21,366 --> 00:28:24,036
