524
00:33:49,736 --> 00:33:51,070
No problem.

525
00:33:51,071 --> 00:33:52,989
[watch beeps]

526
00:33:57,536 --> 00:34:00,372
Ready for this? It's a little creepy.

527
00:34:01,414 --> 00:34:03,082
[HOOVEY] Every eight hours I got to train

528
00:34:03,083 --> 00:34:06,127
