529
00:34:07,087 --> 00:34:09,296
If not, they're all over the place

530
00:34:09,297 --> 00:34:11,675
and eventually they'll just shut down.

531
00:34:12,175 --> 00:34:14,176
But... you're okay, right?

532
00:34:14,177 --> 00:34:17,555
Well... I look like a complete freakazoid,

533
00:34:17,556 --> 00:34:19,473
