538
00:34:29,109 --> 00:34:31,193
You know, I'm not much on sports,

539
00:34:31,194 --> 00:34:34,029
but I've kinda got this
whole school thing down.

540
00:34:34,030 --> 00:34:37,408
If you need help getting caught
up, or anything, I'm here.

541
00:34:37,409 --> 00:34:38,367
I would like that.

542
00:34:38,368 --> 00:34:39,410
Yeah!

543
00:34:39,411 --> 00:34:43,373
But... can I ask you a really
embarrassing question first?

544
00:34:44,165 --> 00:34:45,291
Okay.

545
00:34:45,292 --> 00:34:48,420
Could you please help me get
this stupid locker open?

546
00:34:49,546 --> 00:34:51,506
What's your combination?

547
00:34:54,301 --> 00:34:55,468
Thirty-five.

548
00:34:55,719 --> 00:34:57,136
Thirty-five.

549
00:34:57,137 --> 00:34:58,137
Fourteen.

550
00:34:58,680 --> 00:35:00,097
Fourteen.

551
00:35:00,098 --> 00:35:01,098
Twelve.

552
00:35:01,391 --> 00:35:02,517
Twelve.

553
00:35:03,602 --> 00:35:05,020
There we go!

554
00:35:05,562 --> 00:35:09,482
It's the deductibles and unpaid
expenses that's killing us.

555
00:35:10,734 --> 00:35:12,360
Let's have it.

556
00:35:14,321 --> 00:35:17,197
The city's helping, but it's not enough.

557
00:35:17,198 --> 00:35:20,952
That's... can't be right.

558
00:35:21,578 --> 00:35:25,540
It's a lot of money Elliott.
We're on the hook for it.

559
00:35:27,626 --> 00:35:29,544
Okay.

560
00:35:31,004 --> 00:35:33,380
Well... we got two foals
coming in a few months...

561
00:35:33,381 --> 00:35:34,381
that's five grand right there.

562
00:35:34,382 --> 00:35:35,549
<i>That?“ keep our heads above water</i>

563
00:35:35,550 --> 00:35:37,718
