564
00:35:37,719 --> 00:35:39,511
Alright?

565
00:35:39,512 --> 00:35:41,097
Okay.

566
00:35:42,474 --> 00:35:45,434
[HOOVEY] (struggling) ...at the...
Bat-tle of... G-Gettys...

567
00:35:45,435 --> 00:35:46,310
[RUTH] Gettysburg.

568
00:35:46,311 --> 00:35:47,353
Gettysburg.

569
00:35:47,354 --> 00:35:49,481
That's right. We're getting there.

570
00:35:52,317 --> 00:35:53,233
[Hoovey growls]

571
00:35:53,234 --> 00:35:54,568
[slams book]

572
00:35:54,569 --> 00:35:57,112
[HOOVEY] Right. I can't see straight.

573
00:35:57,113 --> 00:35:59,698
I can't read. Or or or walk.

574
00:35:59,699 --> 00:36:01,742
And my left side has a mind of its own.

575
00:36:01,743 --> 00:36:04,536
I don't know what "there"
you're talking about Mom,

576
00:36:04,537 --> 00:36:06,956
but I'm not so sure I'm going to like it.

577
00:36:09,668 --> 00:36:13,004
I heard you arguing on the phone.

578
00:36:13,338 --> 00:36:15,674
Was it... a bill collector?

579
00:36:18,510 --> 00:36:20,053
Yes.

580
00:36:20,679 --> 00:36:24,723
It was. But she wished she hadn't called

581
00:36:24,724 --> 00:36:27,018
after I got through with her.

582
00:36:28,019 --> 00:36:29,019
I'm sorry mom...

583
00:36:29,020 --> 00:36:31,647
You and Dad... didn't sign up for this.

584
00:36:31,648 --> 00:36:33,649
<i>[dank of a untens 'm a pan]</i>

585
00:36:33,650 --> 00:36:35,567
Don't you ever say that again.

586
00:36:35,568 --> 00:36:37,195
Do you understand?

587
00:36:38,113 --> 00:36:39,531
Look at me.

588
00:36:41,741 --> 00:36:43,701
[RUTH] You didn't do this.

589
00:36:43,702 --> 00:36:47,329
