"sorry" I wanna hear on it.

597
00:37:18,403 --> 00:37:20,571
You got that?

598
00:37:20,572 --> 00:37:22,323
Yes ma'am.

599
00:37:26,035 --> 00:37:27,996
Okay. Let's do it again.

600
00:37:29,581 --> 00:37:33,125
{music}

601
00:37:33,126 --> 00:37:35,169
[whistle]

602
00:37:35,170 --> 00:37:37,464
[chatter]

603
00:37:40,967 --> 00:37:42,177
Keep it moving!

604
00:37:46,055 --> 00:37:48,223
[COACH WILSON] Stay low now... stay low.

605
00:37:48,224 --> 00:37:50,726
Alright... push it push it push it!

606
00:37:50,727 --> 00:37:53,188
Stay low. Stay low!

607
00:37:53,521 --> 00:37:55,397
Hey Hoov... nice patch!

608
00:37:55,398 --> 00:37:58,026
[teammates greet Hoovey]

609
00:37:59,569 --> 00:38:01,613
Hey guys. What's up Scoot?

610
00:38:03,990 --> 00:38:06,326
[COACH WILSON] Alright boys... water up.

611
00:38:08,244 --> 00:38:09,077
Coach.

612
00:38:09,078 --> 00:38:10,497
[COACH WILSON] Yeah.

613
00:38:11,122 --> 00:38:14,082
I... just came to say...
it may take awhile,

614
00:38:14,083 --> 00:38:16,460
but I want back on this team.

615
00:38:16,461 --> 00:38:19,130
Oh... you were never off the team son.

616
00:38:20,256 --> 00:38:22,549
'Til you get your game back on...

617
00:38:22,550 --> 00:38:24,384
how about doing some coaching?

618
00:38:24,385 --> 00:38:26,053
Sir?

619
00:38:26,054 --> 00:38:28,515
Well I mean I can't see
everything out there.

620
00:38:29,724 --> 00:38:33,686
Tomorrow at three... Coach Elliott.
See you there.

621
00:38:34,395 --> 00:38:35,562
[HOOVEY] Yes sir!

622
00:38:35,563 --> 00:38:37,564
[COACH WILSON] Oh... and HOOV...

623
00:38:37,565 --> 00:38:41,110
