00:38:55,542 --> 00:38:56,500
[COACH WILSON] Wait a minute.

625
00:38:56,501 --> 00:38:59,087
Hoovey... Come on over here.

626
00:39:05,969 --> 00:39:06,844
[PHOTOGRAPHER] Hey thirty-three,

627
00:39:06,845 --> 00:39:08,346
