eat again until Friday.

751
00:47:49,408 --> 00:47:53,078
<i>[JEFF] Good. That?“ save us a grocery run.</i>

752
00:47:53,079 --> 00:47:55,498
[JEN] This is a tough one... isn't it?

753
00:47:57,041 --> 00:47:58,541
[JEFF] What do you mean?

754
00:47:58,542 --> 00:48:01,378
Hello? I'm eighteen...

755
00:48:01,379 --> 00:48:03,046
not eight.

756
00:48:03,047 --> 00:48:04,715
I know what's going on.

757
00:48:06,384 --> 00:48:08,885
Your mother and I are so proud of you, hun.

758
00:48:08,886 --> 00:48:11,054
You're a beautiful...?

759
00:48:11,055 --> 00:48:12,889
Thanks.

760
00:48:12,890 --> 00:48:15,350
You're changing the subject.

761
00:48:15,351 --> 00:48:17,602
All right, that's it...

762
00:48:17,603 --> 00:48:18,937
I'm cutting you out of the will.

763
00:48:18,938 --> 00:48:20,397
[laughs]

764
00:48:20,398 --> 00:48:22,732
You'll get nothing and like it.
The way it's gonna have to be.

765
00:48:22,733 --> 00:48:25,360
[laughs]

766
00:48:25,361 --> 00:48:27,404
You remember when I used to get scared

767
00:48:27,405 --> 00:48:29,864
