770
00:48:32,410 --> 00:48:33,661
"Don't be afraid."

771
00:48:34,703 --> 00:48:38,039
Well, we were never afraid before.

772
00:48:38,040 --> 00:48:39,707
How did you get so wise?

773
00:48:39,708 --> 00:48:40,542
From Mom. From Mom, yes...

774
00:48:40,543 --> 00:48:42,043
[shocked gasp] Hurting feelings.

775
00:48:42,044 --> 00:48:44,671
Awwww.

776
00:48:44,672 --> 00:48:46,257
Thanks for the day, honey.

777
00:48:48,050 --> 00:48:49,926
Let's go.

778
00:48:49,927 --> 00:48:53,012
[JEN] Dad... Dad? The car's way over there.

779
00:48:53,013 --> 00:48:54,932
[JEFF] Mine is. This one's yours.

780
