1307
01:18:32,333 --> 01:18:33,416
Tell me about it.

1308
01:18:33,417 --> 01:18:34,751
Just watch your back.

1309
01:18:34,752 --> 01:18:35,752
All right.

1310
01:18:37,463 --> 01:18:38,589
Thanks, Doc.

1311
01:18:44,637 --> 01:18:46,388
He'll be fine.

1312
01:18:55,731 --> 01:18:56,731
Hey.

1313
01:18:57,816 --> 01:18:59,192
Hey.

1314
01:18:59,193 --> 01:19:00,485
Be careful.

1315
01:19:00,486 --> 01:19:01,486
Why?

1316
01:19:01,487 --> 01:19:03,238
I've got gravitas.

1317
01:19:03,239 --> 01:19:04,573
[BOTH quietly chuckle]

1318
01:19:06,659 --> 01:19:08,117
Get out there.

1319
01:19:08,118 --> 01:19:09,203
Hey, Mike...

1320
01:19:11,789 --> 01:19:13,456
[ANNOUNCER] And Derek Jones
