1323
01:19:21,257 --> 01:19:23,133
Elliot pressing back with the Spartans.

1324
01:19:25,427 --> 01:19:27,595
But Jones is all over him!

1325
01:19:27,596 --> 01:19:30,265
You've got to give it up for
these undefeated Cobras

1326
01:19:30,266 --> 01:19:32,226
and their defense.

1327
01:19:36,146 --> 01:19:37,605
But Elliot finds an opening...

1328
01:19:37,606 --> 01:19:39,399
and it's up for three!

1329
01:19:39,400 --> 01:19:41,443
And the Spartans trail by one.

1330
01:19:42,611 --> 01:19:44,195
Jones to number twenty...

1331
01:19:44,196 --> 01:19:45,614
Score!

1332
01:19:49,326 --> 01:19:50,785
Derek Jones for the three!

1333
01:19:50,786 --> 01:19:54,247
[CROWD cheers]

1334
01:19:54,248 --> 01:19:55,498
[ANNOUNCER] As we begin the fourth quarter

1335
01:19:55,499 --> 01:19:58,293
the undefeated Cobras are
really beginning to dominate

1336
01:19:58,294 --> 01:19:59,336
here tonight.

1337
01:20:03,465 --> 01:20:05,383
Our Olympia Spartans trail by ten

1338
01:20:05,384 --> 01:20:07,303
with less than four minutes to play.

1339
01:20:10,472 --> 01:20:12,099
Donovan Oaks picks up the rebound...

1340
01:20:15,352 --> 01:20:16,520
To Jared White...

1341
01:20:17,688 --> 01:20:19,606
Score Spartans!

1342
01:20:23,152 --> 01:20:23,943
Jones...

1343
01:20:23,944 --> 01:20:25,321
A great steal by the Spartans!

1344
01:20:28,365 --> 01:20:29,657
Jared White scores again!

1345
01:20:29,658 --> 01:20:31,160
Oh yes!

1346
01:20:32,536 --> 01:20:33,746
Elliot to Oakes...

1347
01:20:35,122 --> 01:20:36,540
Score Spartans!

1348
01:20:37,499 --> 01:20:39,751
Ladies and Gentlemen it looks
like our whole team has

1349
01:20:39,752 --> 01:20:42,087
some last minute surprises in store.

1350
01:20:44,173 --> 01:20:46,549
Hoovey Elliot... to Oakes.

1351
01:20:46,550 --> 01:20:47,592
Score Spartans!

1352
01:20:47,593 --> 01:20:49,761
[whistle]

1353
01:20:49,762 --> 01:20:52,638
Technical foul, you twelve.

1354
01:20:52,639 --> 01:20:53,514
Oh Jeff.

1355
01:20:53,515 --> 01:20:55,725
This game has clearly
reached a boiling point

1356
01:20:55,726 --> 01:20:57,603
for the Cobras' Derek Jones.

1357
01:20:59,188 --> 01:21:01,522
But Hoovey's okay, ladies and gentlemen.

1358
01:21:01,523 --> 01:21:02,524
He's okay.

1359
01:21:04,693 --> 01:21:06,277
[DONOVAN] You hit him again,
I'm gonna break your jaw.

1360
01:21:06,278 --> 01:21:06,986
You understand me?

1361
01:21:06,987 --> 01:21:08,154
[whistles]

1362
01:21:08,155 --> 01:21:12,117
[PLAYERS yell, REFS whistle]

1363
01:21:17,039 --> 01:21:18,581
[ANNOUNCER] The Spartans'
Eric Hoovey Elliot

1364
01:21:18,582 --> 01:21:21,585
is up for the technical free
throws that could tie this game.

1365
01:21:31,053 --> 01:21:32,637
[CROWD cheers]

1366
01:21:32,638 --> 01:21:34,598
The Spartans trail by just one point.

1367
01:21:38,811 --> 01:21:40,228
[COACH WILSON] Yes!
[ANNOUNCER] And it's good!

1368
01:21:40,229 --> 01:21:42,563
We have a tied game here, with
just over a minute to play.

1369
01:21:42,564 --> 01:21:44,232
[whistle]

1370
01:21:44,233 --> 01:21:47,276
And Coach Wilson puts
number five, Aaron Taylor,

1371
01:21:47,277 --> 01:21:47,902
in for Elliot.

1372
01:21:47,903 --> 01:21:49,321
[RUTH] We made it.

1373
01:21:51,323 --> 01:21:52,824
Good job young man.

1374
01:21:52,825 --> 01:21:53,783
Now you're done for tonight.

1375
01:21:53,784 --> 01:21:55,493
If only he had a little
more gas in his tank.

1376
01:21:55,494 --> 01:21:56,619
Yeah, don't push your luck.

1377
01:21:56,620 --> 01:21:58,454
This whole thing's a miracle.

1378
01:21:58,455 --> 01:21:59,540
You know that?

1379
01:22:01,417 --> 01:22:02,375
Coach?

1380
01:22:02,376 --> 01:22:04,293
Yeah?

1381
01:22:04,294 --> 01:22:06,255
Give me a minute. I just need a breather.

1382
01:22:10,759 --> 01:22:11,717
No sir.

1383
01:22:11,718 --> 01:22:14,303
You did your job and
Donovan's got the hot hand.

1384
01:22:14,304 --> 01:22:15,597
We can handle it.

1385
01:22:17,683 --> 01:22:21,645
{music}

1386
01:22:51,300 --> 01:22:52,508
