Just one more minute.

1387
01:22:52,509 --> 01:22:54,094
I know I can do this.

1388
01:23:00,601 --> 01:23:02,643
[whistle]

1389
01:23:02,644 --> 01:23:04,564
[ANNOUNCER] Personal foul
with number forty-one.

1390
01:23:11,487 --> 01:23:13,322
He... He's not very nice.

1391
01:23:16,116 --> 01:23:17,617
[ANNOUNCER] Time out Spartans.

1392
01:23:17,618 --> 01:23:19,660
You sure you're done?

1393
01:23:19,661 --> 01:23:20,453
No way, dude.

1394
01:23:20,454 --> 01:23:21,496
[COACH WILSON] Ugh.

1395
01:23:21,497 --> 01:23:23,206
All right.

1396
01:23:23,207 --> 01:23:24,123
[HOOVEY] Coach?... [COACH WILSON] Yeah?

1397
01:23:24,124 --> 01:23:26,542
[HOOVEY] I can go.

1398
01:23:26,543 --> 01:23:28,253
I can go.

1399
01:23:30,297 --> 01:23:31,756
Your call.

1400
01:23:31,757 --> 01:23:33,257
Oh no you don't.

1401
01:23:33,258 --> 01:23:34,800
You're not putting this on me.

1402
01:23:34,801 --> 01:23:36,553
Yeah. I am.

1403
01:23:45,062 --> 01:23:46,646
Coach, I'm in.

1404
01:23:46,647 --> 01:23:48,148
All right, go check yourself in.

1405
01:23:51,151 --> 01:23:52,277
Thirty-three.

1406
01:23:55,656 --> 01:23:57,114
Now look...

1407
01:23:57,115 --> 01:23:59,283
You won't remember the
score like you remember

1408
01:23:59,284 --> 01:24:02,620
what happens in the next
forty-five seconds of your life.

1409
01:24:02,621 --> 01:24:04,413
Give everybody here
something to believe in.

1410
01:24:04,414 --> 01:24:05,790
Do your job.

1411
01:24:05,791 --> 01:24:07,291
All right, we on three.

1412
01:24:07,292 --> 01:24:08,417
One, two, three...

1413
01:24:08,418 --> 01:24:09,252
[ALL] We!

1414
01:24:09,253 --> 01:24:11,128
Let's go!

1415
01:24:11,129 --> 01:24:13,589
That's the best pass I
ever saw, Hoovey-man.

1416
01:24:13,590 --> 01:24:14,799
Let's take it.

1417
01:24:14,800 --> 01:24:16,301
Go Spartans!

1418
01:24:55,674 --> 01:24:56,507
[JEFF] That's it.

1419
01:24:56,508 --> 01:24:58,176
Let's shoot it, son.

1420
01:25:08,562 --> 01:25:12,189
[sound muffles]

1421
01:25:12,190 --> 01:25:13,316
[whistle]

1422
01:25:13,317 --> 01:25:15,318
[buzzer]

1423
01:25:15,319 --> 01:25:17,653
[CROWD yells]

1424
01:25:17,654 --> 01:25:18,487
[DONOVAN] That's enough with all that, man.

1425
01:25:18,488 --> 01:25:19,280
[whistles]

1426
01:25:19,281 --> 01:25:22,158
[whistles, commotion]
[JEFF] Hoovey! Hoovey!

1427
01:25:22,159 --> 01:25:24,328
"[JEFF] Hoovey! Hoovey!

1428
01:25:25,495 --> 01:25:26,747
You with me, son?

1429
01:25:31,209 --> 01:25:32,544
Hoove!

1430
01:25:36,048 --> 01:25:37,424
Are you with me, boy?

1431
01:25:40,135 --> 01:25:41,762
[voice breaks] Hoove, come on.

1432
01:25:44,640 --> 01:25:47,642
Did you see that left move, big boy?

1433
01:25:47,643 --> 01:25:49,269
Yeah I saw it, Pinto.

1434
01:25:51,146 --> 01:25:54,774
[CROWD cheers]

1435
01:25:54,775 --> 01:25:56,234
[HOOVEY] I'm okay, Mom.

1436
01:26:09,206 --> 01:26:10,790
Did go in, didn't it?

1437
01:26:10,791 --> 01:26:12,124
Nothing but net.

1438
01:26:12,125 --> 01:26:14,251
That was my shot, too.

1439
01:26:14,252 --> 01:26:16,629
[REF] If you think they can't
shoot, you can use a player

1440
01:26:16,630 --> 01:26:18,590
from the bench, Coach. Not from the floor.

1441
01:26:22,094 --> 01:26:23,636
[HOOVEY] Coach.

1442
01:26:23,637 --> 01:26:25,471
This is my shot.

1443
01:26:25,472 --> 01:26:26,722
<i>Mine.</i>

1444
01:26:26,723 --> 01:26:29,266
Okay then...

1445
01:26:29,267 --> 01:26:31,435
drain it.

1446
01:26:31,436 --> 01:26:33,813
[whistle]

1447
01:26:33,814 --> 01:26:36,148
Were you really gonna hit that guy?

1448
01:26:36,149 --> 01:26:37,650
I still might.

1449
01:26:37,651 --> 01:26:39,151
Don't bother.

1450
01:26:39,152 --> 01:26:40,612
I'm finishing this right now.

1451
01:27:01,216 --> 01:27:03,718
