there when I brought him home

1452
01:27:03,719 --> 01:27:05,511
some helmets to try out.

1453
01:27:05,512 --> 01:27:06,303
[laughs]

1454
01:27:06,304 --> 01:27:08,347
You see, the thing is...

1455
01:27:08,348 --> 01:27:10,474
eventually...

1456
01:27:10,475 --> 01:27:14,438
we all just have to let go
and get in that wheelbarrow.

1457
01:27:15,647 --> 01:27:18,483
Or we'll never get to the other side.

1458
01:27:20,777 --> 01:27:23,529
Because believing...

1459
01:27:23,530 --> 01:27:25,490
makes it possible.

1460
01:27:26,742 --> 01:27:29,326
Faith...

1461
01:27:29,327 --> 01:27:31,204
makes it real.

1462
01:27:38,086 --> 01:27:42,048
[CROWD cheers]

1463
01:28:40,774 --> 01:28:44,736
{music}

1464
